title: Life is Like a Puzzle
itunes:title: Life is Like a Puzzle
description:
Episode 494 - In life sometimes we get what we want and sometimes we don't. Either way, we should learn to arrange whatever pieces we get. To sit and complain about the pieces does not change anything. Therefore, we should get good at accepting life and using our skills to make our lives better. In this episode, I teach you how to do that.
